snippet.title: Sicko Sanctum Megahecks - Release Trailer
snippet.description:
After a year of development, Sicko Sanctum is once and for all, complete. Fight your way through code hell in Sicko Sanctum Megahecks, a score attack movement shooter with surreal aesthetics now available on itch.io for $2.99. (link below)
https://jake-stevenson.itch.io/sicko-sanctum-megahecks

Also check out Bonkaheck Ballin: Inquiry of Absolution, a remake of the first complete game I ever made out now! (Trailer link below)
https://youtu.be/SjJV6_IZFeA
